      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from a man, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘There are no omissions (allowed) in Al-Maghrib and Al-Fajr (<span class=\"iTxt\">Salāt</span>s)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from Yunus from a man who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘There is no confusion (acceptable) in al-Maghrib and morning Salah (prayer).”’ "
        ]
      }
